name: LifeWatch observatory data: reference collection of unique observations in the Belgian Part of the North Sea
description: In the framework of the Lifewatch marineobservatory nine fixed stations on the Belgian Part of the North Sea (BPNS) are visited on a monthly basis,and 17 fixed stations on a seasonal basis,using the RV SimonStevin. This dataset holds records of uniqueobservations in the Belgian Part of the North Sea, which are not collected on a continous base('loose observations') anddo not fit into any ofthe other described LifeWatch Datasets.
